Cathy Yang - Final 

l          Toggle lighting+shadows on/off
p	   Pause
[]         Lower/rise light
()	   Move light left/right along the azimuth
arrows     Change view angle
PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
0          Reset view angle

ESC        Exit

Added a flag to the mailbox since the last review, Happy Birthday Canada (7/1). Faster "smoke".

SHADOWS. My LORD those must have taken at least 9 of the 32 hours I spent on this. I opted for shadows instead of the first person. It seemed more difficult than first person, and the whole thing just seemed really wrong without them.  

(My VM is on its last legs, and I'm kind of proud of that too. "Did you know I almost killed a VM?")
